data.description: Beautiful corner lot home on a quiet cul-de-sac located in one of Goddard's sought-after communities!  Welcome yourself to this 3 bed, 2 bath, 3-car garage single family home with 1,796 sq ft of spacious interiors sitting on a large 0.22 acre lot.  Gorgeous laminate wood flooring creates a sense of luxury and comfort in the living room while also enjoying the natural light that flows in through the large window.  The kitchen is located directly off the living area, supplying plenty of cabinetry as well as an island; perfect for hosting family and friends.  The dining area is surrounded by three large windows with access to the open deck in the private, fenced in backyard.  The carpeted master bedroom boasts a walk-in closet, as well as access to the Hollywood bath in the hall.  One more bedroom completes the living space on the main level.  A dedicated laundry room by the garage entry provides additional efficiency to the layout of the main floor.  Walking downstairs, you will find a fully finished basement that provides not only a third bedroom with a walk-in closet and second full bath, but is also complete with a fully carpeted, open area perfect for a family room or entertainment lounge.  A newer water softener is a huge bonus that is also included in the sale.  Live in the unbeatable location with access to community amenities and just off Route 400/W Kellogg Ave.  Very close to shopping areas, dining spots, and high-ranking schools.  ***Agents, please include in any offer in paragraph 32 “Seller is a licensed agent in the State of Kansas”***Call us to come and see this beautiful home today!
